race.comment: I AM BRAVE (1) two runs back have been okay after drawing poorly. Was doing her best work late when fifth over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Can race a little closer here and return to winning form. MIGNONETTE (2) well bred mare looking for this trip and further now. Held her ground through the line on resumption when sixth over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Watch for her late. FAST TRACK (3) returned for her second preparation with a gritty fourth over 1400m at Hawkesbury with the 58kg. Will need luck early from the draw and good enough to test some of these. HARD KNOCK LIFE (8) rounded them up effortlessly two-back when getting off the mark at Taree. Snagged back from the wide barrier and failed to get into the contest when last over 1400m at Coonabarabran. Improver with the claim from the inside gate. OH DEER (4) improving mare starting to hit her straps. Gets in light again and stays in the calculations.
